{"type":"message","id":"0ab0d9ee","parentId":"166c3347","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:13:37.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_e00d12de-ffa2-453a-93a5-f47f98684414","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -50 /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/rag_abroadworks/AGENT_MANAGEMENT_RESEARCH.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":39522,"output":100,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39622,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774008817250}}
{"type":"message","id":"729218d4","parentId":"0ab0d9ee","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:13:37.263Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_e00d12de-ffa2-453a-93a5-f47f98684414","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AI Agent Management Best Practices - Research Summary\n\n_Compiled: 2026-03-19 | Sources: Deloitte, Microsoft, n8n, Kubiya, Kanerika_\n\n---\n\n## 1. Orchestration Patterns\n\n### Three Main Patterns\n\n| Pattern | Best For | Example |\n|---------|----------|---------|\n| **Hierarchical** | Complex workflows with clear escalation | Supervisor agent routes tasks to specialists |\n| **Collaborative** | Peer-to-peer, equal agents | Multi-agent research teams |\n| **Handoff** | Human-in-the-loop, expert escalation | Customer support → specialist |\n\n### Key Frameworks\n\n- **LangChain** — Production-grade, deep integrations\n- **CrewAI** — Role-based multi-agent workflows\n- **AutoGen (Microsoft)** — Open-source multi-agent systems\n- **n8n** — No-code workflow automation\n- **Botpress** — Developer-first, no vendor lock-in\n\n---\n\n## 2. Communication Protocols\n\n### Emerging Standards (2025-2026)\n\n| Protocol | Leader | Purpose |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| **MCP** | Anthropic | Agent ↔ Tools |\n| **A2A** | Google | Agent ↔ Agent |\n| **AGNTCY** | Cisco | Enterprise agent coordination |\n\n**Prediction:** By 2027, 2-3 protocols will dominate; others converge or fade.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Management Platforms & Observability\n\n### Essential Capabilities\n\n- **Agent telemetry**: Latency, error rates, token usage\n- **Guardrails**: Unusual behavior detection, risk mitigation\n- **Guardian agents**: Task ownership + governance of other agents\n- **Audit trails**: Inter-agent messages, explanations, traceability\n\n### Build vs Buy"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7,"aggregated":"# AI Agent Management Best Practices - Research Summary\n\n_Compiled: 2026-03-19 | Sources: Deloitte, Microsoft, n8n, Kubiya, Kanerika_\n\n---\n\n## 1. Orchestration Patterns\n\n### Three Main Patterns\n\n| Pattern | Best For | Example |\n|---------|----------|---------|\n| **Hierarchical** | Complex workflows with clear escalation | Supervisor agent routes tasks to specialists |\n| **Collaborative** | Peer-to-peer, equal agents | Multi-agent research teams |\n| **Handoff** | Human-in-the-loop, expert escalation | Customer support → specialist |\n\n### Key Frameworks\n\n- **LangChain** — Production-grade, deep integrations\n- **CrewAI** — Role-based multi-agent workflows\n- **AutoGen (Microsoft)** — Open-source multi-agent systems\n- **n8n** — No-code workflow automation\n- **Botpress** — Developer-first, no vendor lock-in\n\n---\n\n## 2. Communication Protocols\n\n### Emerging Standards (2025-2026)\n\n| Protocol | Leader | Purpose |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| **MCP** | Anthropic | Agent ↔ Tools |\n| **A2A** | Google | Agent ↔ Agent |\n| **AGNTCY** | Cisco | Enterprise agent coordination |\n\n**Prediction:** By 2027, 2-3 protocols will dominate; others converge or fade.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Management Platforms & Observability\n\n### Essential Capabilities\n\n- **Agent telemetry**: Latency, error rates, token usage\n- **Guardrails**: Unusual behavior detection, risk mitigation\n- **Guardian agents**: Task ownership + governance of other agents\n- **Audit trails**: Inter-agent messages, explanations, traceability\n\n### Build vs Buy","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774008817261}}
