{"type":"message","id":"53bef8a4","parentId":"4befbc36","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:42:46.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_3e9e6dc4-18df-4d8c-9f9c-d4b98784dd8d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -hi \"by \\|author\" /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/rag_abroadworks/clean_md/hiring-challenges.md | head -10"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":36113,"output":93,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36206,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774010566306}}
{"type":"message","id":"004ae870","parentId":"53bef8a4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:42:46.318Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_3e9e6dc4-18df-4d8c-9f9c-d4b98784dd8d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Resume evaluation and qualification standards differ by country\nBusinesses can overcome many of the inherent biases of interviewing an overseas candidate by creating scorecards and matrices where they identify characteristics that are the most important to the role. By quantifying what they want, they can potentially eliminate unnecessary judgement and find the best candidate, regardless of the differences.\nLabor offshoring can also help a business drastically reduce its labor expenses. Depending on the position, a business can save roughly 80% on labor costs. Businesses can find the most qualified employees capable of meeting any of their needs by going offshore. Virtual assistants, accountants, marketing, graphic designers, and even management can be found offshore for significantly less."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7,"aggregated":"Resume evaluation and qualification standards differ by country\nBusinesses can overcome many of the inherent biases of interviewing an overseas candidate by creating scorecards and matrices where they identify characteristics that are the most important to the role. By quantifying what they want, they can potentially eliminate unnecessary judgement and find the best candidate, regardless of the differences.\nLabor offshoring can also help a business drastically reduce its labor expenses. Depending on the position, a business can save roughly 80% on labor costs. Businesses can find the most qualified employees capable of meeting any of their needs by going offshore. Virtual assistants, accountants, marketing, graphic designers, and even management can be found offshore for significantly less.","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774010566316}}
