{"type":"message","id":"ededf11b","parentId":"a7818b69","timestamp":"2026-03-20T17:40:00.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Whisper community models exist for Ollama:\n\n```\nollama pull dimavz/whisper-tiny   # ~39MB\nollama pull karanchopda333/whisper  # base model\n```\n\n**But** — these are transcribed versions, not native Whisper. Performance varies.\n\n**Simpler path:** Install Whisper directly (Python + faster-whisper), then pipe to Ollama:\n\n```bash\npip install faster-whisper\n```\n\nThen I'd need a script to: receive audio → transcribe with Whisper → feed text to me.\n\nWant me to install Whisper and set up the pipeline?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":46197,"output":152,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46349,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774028400209}}
